var book = {
	"name": "Jingpynpaw",
	"numChapters": 22,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka jingpynpaw U Jisu Khrist, ïa kaba U Blei u la ai ha u, ban pyni ha ki shakri jong u ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba dei ban jia long shen; bad haba u la phah da u angel jong u, u la pyntip ïa ka ha u Ïoannis u shakri jong u,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> uba la phla ïa ka ktien U Blei, bad ïa ka jingphla U Jisu Khrist, ïa kita kiei kiei baroh keiñ kiba u la ïohi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Suk uta uba pule, bad kita kiba ïohsngew ïa ki ktien jong kane ka jingïathuhlypa, bad kiba sumar ïa kita kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba la thoh ha ka; namar kata ka Ïa ka la jan.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Ïoannis, ha kita ki hynñiew balang kiba ha Asia: To long ka jingaiei ha phi bad ka jingsuk, na uta uba long bad uba la ju long bad u ban sa wan; bad na kita ki hynñiew ki mynsiem kiba long ha khmat ka khet jong u;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad na U Jisu Khrist, uba long U Nongphla ïa uba lah ban shaniah, ïa uba la kha nyngkong na ki baïap, bad U Nongsynshar ki syiem ka pyrthei. Ha uta uba la ieit ïa ngi, bad uba la sait ïa ngi na ki pop jong ngi ha ka snam jong u hi;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u la pynlong ïa ngi ki syiem bad ki lyngdoh ha U Blei bad U Kpa jong u; ha u to long ka burom bad ka jingsynshar sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut: Amen.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ha khmih, u wan bad ki lyoh, bad ka khmat baroh kan ïohi ïa u, bad kita ruh kiba la sum ïa u; bad ki jaid bynriew baroh jong ka pyrthei kin ïalynñiar lympat namar jong u. Kumta shisha: Amen.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Nga long ma nga U Alpha bad U Omega,” ong U Trai uba U Blei, uta uba long bad uba ju long bad uta u ban sa wan, uta U Badonbor Baroh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ma nga u Ïoannis, uba u parabangeit jong phi, bad u nongïaïoh bynta lem ha ka jingjynjar, bad ha ka hima bad ka jingïaishah U Jisu Khrist, nga la don ha kata ka 'dewlynnong ïa kaba la khot “Patmos”, na ka bynta ka ktien U Blei bad na ka bynta ka jingphla ïa U Jisu Khrist.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Nga la long ha U Mynsiem ha ka sngi U Trai, bad nga la ïohsngew na shadien jong nga ïa ka ktien bajam kum ka turoi,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ka da ong, “Nga long ma nga U Alpha bad U Omega, u banyngkong bad u bakhatduh: ïa kaba me ïohi, to thoh ha ka kitab, bad to phah ha kita ki hynñiew balang; sha Ephesos, bad sha Smyrna, bad sha Pergamos, bad sha Thiateira, bad sha Sardis, bad sha Philadelphia, bad sha Laodikaïa.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te nga la phai ban ïoh khmih thuh ïa kata ka ktien kaba la kren ha nga; te haba nga la phai, nga la ïohi hynñiew ki dieng pynïeng sharak ksiar;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad hapdeng kita ki hynñiew ki dieng pynïeng sharak, ïa uwei uba kum U Khun u briew, uba la kup jaiñkup haduh ki kjat, bad uba la panpoh ka jingpanpoh ksiar ha ki jymbuiñ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ka khlieh jong u bad u shñiuh jong u kiba lieh kum u 'ñiuh langbrot balieh kat ka ïor keiñ; bad ki khmat jong u kum ka thylliej ding;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad ki kjat jong u kum ka rnong baphyrnai, kum haba la thang ïa ki ha ka lawar ding; bad ka ktien jong u kum ka jingsawa shibun ki um.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la don ha ka kti kamon jong u hynñiew ki khlur; bad na ka shyntur jong u, ka da mih noh ka waitlam ba ar liang syrti banep; bad ka khmat jong u, ka la long kum haba ka sngi ka tyngshaiñ ha ka borbah jong ka.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad haba nga la ïohi ïa u, nga la kyllon sbak ha ki kjat jong u kum uba ïap. U te u la buh ïa ka kti kamon jong u ha nga, u da ong, “To wat sheptieng; nga long ma nga u banyngkong bad u bakhatduh, bad uta U Ba-im;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad nga la jia long u baïap, te ha khmih, nga long u ba-im sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut, bad nga don keiñ ki shabi ka dujok bad ka jingïap.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Namar kata, to thoh ïa kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba me la ïohi, bad ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba long, bad ïa kiei kiei ruh ki ban sa long hadien kine;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ïa ka jingmaïan shaphang kita ki hynñiew ki khlur ïa kiba me la ïohi ha ka kti kamon jong nga, bad ïa kita ki hynñiew ki dieng pynïeng sharak ksiar. Kita ki hynñiew ki khlur ki long ki angel jong kita ki hynñiew balang, bad kita ki hynñiew ki dieng pynïeng sharak ki long ki hynñiew balang."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ha uta u angel jong ka balang ha Ephesos to thoh: Ïa kine kiei kiei ruh u ong uta uba bat ïa kita ki hynñiew ki khlur ha ka kti kamon jong u, uta uba ïaid hapdeng kita ki hynñiew ki dieng pynïeng sharak ksiar:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “ ‘Nga ithuh ïa ki jingleh jong pha, bad ïa ka jingleh minot bad ka jingïaishah jong pha, bad ba pham lah ban shah shuh ïa ki basniew: bad pha la tynjuh ïit ïa kita kiba ong ba ki long ki apostol, bad kim long, te pha la shem ïa ki, kiba lamler;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad pha don ka jingïaishah bad pha la shah na ka bynta ka kyrteng jong nga, bad pham shym la sngewthait ïan.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, nga don kane kaba pyrshah ïa pha, ba pha la iehnoh noh ïa ka jingieit jong pha ka banyngkong.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> To kynmaw, namar kata, nangno pha la hap noh, bad to kylla-ka-bamut, bad to leh ïa kita ki jingleh ki banyngkong; lymda kumta, nga wan kloi ha pha, bad ngan pynkynriah noh ïa ka dieng pynïeng sharak jong pha na ka jaka jong ka, lada pham kylla-ka-bamut.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, kane pha don, ba pha shun ïa ki jingleh jong kita ki Nikolaita, ïa kiba nga ruh nga shun.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Jar uba don ka shkor, to un sngew ïa kaei ba U Mynsiem u ong ha kita ki balang. Ha uta uba jop, ngan ai ha u ban bam na u dieng jong ka jingim, uba long ha ka paradais U Blei.’ ”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Bad ha uta u angel jong ka balang ha Smyrna to thoh: Ïa kine kiei kiei ruh u ong uta u banyngkong bad u bakhatduh, uba la jia long u baïap, bad u la im pat:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “ ‘Nga ithuh ïa ka jingshahshitom jong pha, bad ïa ka jingduk jong pha (hynrei, pha long ka bariewspah), bad ïa ka jingkrenbeiñ jong kita kiba ong ba ki long ki Jiw, bad kim long, hynrei, ki long ka synagog jong u Soitan.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> To wat sheptieng ïa kita kiei kiei ruh kiba phan sa shah: ha khmih, uta u Soitan un sa bred ïa kiba na phi ha ka ïing byndi, ba yn ïoh tynjuh ïa phi; te phin ïoh ïa ka jingshahshitom shiphew sngi. To long pha kaba ïaineh haduh ka jingïap, bad ngan ai ha pha ïa kata ka pansngiat jong ka jingim.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Jar uba don ka shkor, to un sngew ïa kaei ba U Mynsiem u ong ha kita ki balang. Ïa uta uba jop, yn ym pynsniew na kata ka jingïap ka ba-ar.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Bad ha uta u angel jong ka balang kaba ha Pergamos to thoh: Ïa kine kiei kiei ruh u ong uta uba don kata ka waitlam kaba ar liang syrti banep:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> “ ‘Nga ithuh hangno pha shong, wat ha kaba don keiñ ka khet u Soitan: bad pha bat skhem ïa ka kyrteng jong nga, bad pham shym la len noh ïa kata ka jingngeit ha nga, wat shisha ha kita ki sngi ha kiba u Antipas u la long u nongphla uba ïaineh jong nga, ïa uba la pynïap noh hapdeng jong phi, ha kaba u Soitan u shong.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, nga don khyndiat kiei kiei ruh pyrshah ïa pha, naba pha don hangta kiba bat ïa kata ka jinghikai u Balaam, uba la hikai ïa u Balak ban buh ïa ka jingjynthut ha khmat kita ki khun Israel, ban bam ïa kiei kiei ruh ba la kñia ïa ki bleithaw, bad ban klim sih.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, pha don ma pha ruh kiba bat kumjuh ïa kata ka jinghikai jong kita ki Nikolaita.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Namar kata, to kylla-ka-bamut; lymda kumta, nga wan kloi ha pha, bad ngan ïaleh thma ïa ki da ka waitlam ka shyntur jong nga.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Jar uba don ka shkor, to un sngew ïa kaei ba U Mynsiem u ong ha kita ki balang. Ha uta uba jop, ngan ai ha u ban bam na kata ka manna ïa kaba la buhrieh noh, bad ngan ai ha u ïa u maw balieh, bad ha uta u maw ïa ka kyrteng bathymmai ïa kaba la thoh, ïa kaba uno uno ruh um ithuh, hynrei, tang uta uba pdiang ïa ka.’ ”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> “Bad ha uta u angel jong ka balang kaba ha Thiateira to thoh: Ïa kine kiei kiei ruh u ong U Khun U Blei, uba don la ki khmat kum ka thylliej ka ding, bad ki kjat jong u kiba kum ka rnong baphyrnai:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “ ‘Nga ithuh ïa ki jingleh jong pha, bad ïa ka jingieit bad ïa ka jingngeit bad ïa ka jingshakri bad ïa ka jingïaishah jong pha; bad ba kita ki jingleh ki bakhatduh jong pha ki long kiba kham bun ïa kita ki banyngkong.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, nga don kane kaba pyrshah ïa pha, naba pha shah ïa kata ka briew ka Jesabel, kaba khot ïa lade “ka nongïathuhlypa”, bad ka hikai bad ka shukor ïa kita ki shakri jong nga ban klim sih, bad ban bam ïa kiei kiei ruh ba la kñia ïa ki bleithaw.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad nga la ai ha ka, ïa ka Ïa babiang ba kan ïoh kylla-ka-bamut; te kam mon ban kylla-ka-bamut na kata kaba klim jong ka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ha khmih, ngan bred ïa ka ha ka jingthiah, bad ïa kita kiba ïaklim bad ka ha ka jingshitom bakhraw, lada kin ym kylla-ka-bamut na kita ki jingleh jong ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ngan pynïap noh ïa ki khun jong ka da ka jingïap; te kita ki balang baroh kin ïatip ba long ma nga uta uba ïit thuh ïa ki khyllai bad ïa ki dohnud; te ngan ai ha phi uwei pa uwei baroh katba kum ki jingleh jong phi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, ha phi nga ong, kata, ha kita kiwei keiñ kiba ha Thiateira, kat ki bymdon kane ka jinghikai, ki bymtip ïa kita ki jingjylliew jong u Soitan, kumba ki ong: “Ngam buh ha phi ïa kawei pat ka jingkit.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, ïa kata kaba phi don, to ïabat skhem tad ynda nga wan.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad uta uba jop, bad uba sumar haduh ka bakut ïa ki jingleh jong nga, ngan ai ha u ka bor halor kita ki kynja bynriew;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad un synshar ïa ki da u dieng synshar nar, kumba pynlwet jin ïa ki khiew jong u nongthaw khiew, kumba nga ruh nga la pdiang na U Kpa jong nga.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ngan ai ha u ïa u khlur-step.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Jar uba don ka shkor, to un sngew ïa kaei ba U Mynsiem u ong ha kita ki balang.’ ”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Bad ha uta u angel jong ka balang kaba ha Sardis to thoh: Ïa kine kiei kiei ruh u ong uta uba don kita ki hynñiew ki Mynsiem U Blei, bad ïa kita ki hynñiew ki khlur: ‘Nga ithuh ïa ki jingleh jong pha, ba pha don ka kyrteng ba pha im, hynrei, pha long ka baïap.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> To long pha kaba sharai, bad to pynskhem ïa kita kiei kiei ruh kiba sah, ki ban sa ïap noh: namar ngam shym shem ïa kita ki jingleh jong pha kiba la dap janai ha khmat U Blei jong nga.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> To kynmaw, namar kata, kumno pha la pdiang bad pha la ïohsngew, bad to ri skhem ïa ka, bad to kylla-ka-bamut. Namar kata, lada pham sharai, ngan wan kum u nongtuh keiñ, te phan ym ïoh tip ha kano ka por ngan wan ha pha.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, pha don khyndiat ki kyrteng wat ha Sardis ki bym shym la pynbit-tngit ïa ki jaiñkup jong ki: te kita kin ïoh ïaid lem bad nga ha ki jaiñkup balieh; naba ki long kiba dei.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Uta uba jop, ïa uta, yn pynkup kumta ha ki jaiñkup balieh; bad ngan ym pyndam noh da lei lei ïa ka kyrteng jong u na ka kitab ka jingim, bad ngan phla keiñ ïa ka kyrteng jong u ha khmat U Kpa jong nga, bad ha khmat ki angel jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Jar uba don ka shkor, to un sngew ïa kaei ba U Mynsiem u ong ha kita ki balang.’ ”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Bad ha uta u angel jong ka balang kaba ha Philadelphia to thoh: Ïa kine kiei kiei ruh u ong uta U Bakhuid, uta U Bashisha, uta uba don u shabi jong u Dabid, uta uba plie, te uno uno ruh um khang, bad u khang te uno uno ruh um plie:",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “ ‘Nga ithuh ïa ki jingleh jong pha; ha khmih, nga la buh ha khmat jong pha ïa ka jingkhang ïa kaba la plie, te uno uno ruh um lah ban khang ïa ka; naba pha don khyndiat khynsoit ka bor, bad pha la ri skhem ïa ka ktien jong nga, bad pham shym la len ïa ka kyrteng jong nga.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ha khmih, nga aiti noh ïa kiba na kata ka synagog u Soitan, kiba ong ba ki long ki Jiw, bad kim long, hynrei, ki lamler; ha khmih, ngan pynleh ïa kita ba kin wan bad ïamane ha khmat ki kjat jong pha, bad ba kin tip ba nga la ieit ma nga ïa pha.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Naba pha la ri skhem ïa ka ktien ka jingïaishah jong nga, te nga ruh ngan ri kyndong ïa pha na kata ka por jong ka jingtynjuh, ka ban sa jia long ha ka pyrthei baroh kawei, ban tynjuh keiñ, ïa kita kiba shong ha ka khyndew.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ha khmih, nga wan kloi: to bat skhem ïa kata kaba pha don, ba uno uno ruh un ym shim ïa ka pansngiat jong pha.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Uta uba jop, ngan pynlong u rijied ïa u ha ka ïing U Blei jong nga, te un ym mih noh shuh shabar: bad ngan thoh halor jong u ïa ka kyrteng U Blei jong nga, bad ïa ka kyrteng jong kata ka nongbah U Blei jong nga, ka Jerusalem bathymmai, kaba wan hiar na bneng na U Blei jong nga, bad ïa kata ka kyrteng jong nga ka bathymmai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Jar uba don ka shkor, to un sngew ïa kaei ba U Mynsiem u ong ha kita ki balang.’ ”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Bad ha uta u angel jong ka balang ha Laodikaïa to thoh: Ïa kine kiei kiei ruh u ong U Amen, U Nongphla U Baïaineh bad U Bashisha, ka jingsdang ka jingpynlong jong U Blei:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “ ‘Nga ithuh keiñ ïa ki jingleh jong pha, ba pham long kaba khriat lymne kaba shit: A nga da kwah dik dik ba phan da long kaba khriat lane kaba shit!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, naba pha long kaba shu syaid, khriat ruh em, shit ruh em, ngan sa prie noh ïa pha na ka shyntur jong nga.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Naba pha ong, “Nga kaba riewbha, bad nga la pynman spah, te ngam don ka jingkyrduh ei ei ruh em,” bad pham tip ba ma pha hi pha long kata kaba lanot khop, bad kaba jynjar sat, bad ka baduk, bad ka bamatlah, bad ka balyngkhuit.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nga pyni buit ha pha ba phan thied na nga ïa ka ksiar ba la phrang ha ka ding, ba phan da ïoh man spah; bad ïa ki jaiñkup balieh, ba phan ïoh kup ïa lade, bad ba kan ym paw kata ka jinglehrain ka jinglyngkhuit jong pha; bad ïa ka jingsleh khmat ban kyllan ïa ki khmat jong pha, ba phan ïohi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kat ïa kiba nga ieit, nga sneng bad nga sympat; to sngewshitrhem namar kata, bad to kylla-ka-bamut.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ha khmih, nga ïeng ha ka jingkhang bad nga tied: lada uno uno ruh un ïohsngew ïa ka ktien jong nga, bad un plie ïa kata ka jingkhang, ngan wan rung hapoh ha u, bad ngan ïakhawai miet lem bad u, bad ma u lem bad nga.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Uta uba jop, ngan ai ha u ban shong lem bad nga halor ka khet jong nga, kumba nga ruh nga la jop, bad nga la shong lem bad U Kpa jong nga halor ka khet jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Jar uba don ka shkor, to un sngew ïa kaei ba U Mynsiem u ong ha kita ki balang.’ ”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, nga la khmih, te ha khmih, ka jingkhang ïa kaba la plie ha bneng; bad kata ka ktien sawa ka banyngkong ïa kaba nga la ïohsngew kum ka turoi ka da kren bad nga, ka da ong, “To ale kiew shane, bad ngan pyni ha me ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba dei ban jia long hadien kane.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh, nga la long ha U Mynsiem; bad ha khmih, ka khet ba la buh ha bneng, bad halor kata ka khet don uwei uba shong.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te uta uba shong u la long haba khmih kum u maw Jasper bad u Sardios: bad la don u simpyllieng baroh sawdong kata ka khet, uba kum u maw Emerald haba peit ïa u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad baroh sawdong kata ka khet ki la don arphew saw tylli ki khet; bad halor ki khet nga la ïohi arphew saw ngut ki tymmen basan kiba shong, kiba la kup ha ki jaiñkup balieh; bad halor ki khlieh jong ki, ki pansngiat ksiar.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad na kata ka khet ki mih noh ki leilieh bad ki jingsawa bad ki pyrthat. Bad la don hynñiew ki sharak ding bathang ha khmat kata ka khet, kiba long kita ki hynñiew ki mynsiem U Blei.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ha khmat kata ka khet ruh, don ka duriaw ïit kum u mawleiñ: Bad hapdeng kata ka khet, bad baroh sawdong kata ka khet saw ki jingthaw ba-im kiba dap da ki khmat sha khmat bad shadien.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te uta u jingthaw u banyngkong u kum u sing, bad uta u jingthaw ba-ar u kum u khun masi, bad uta u jingthaw balai u da don ka khmat kum u briew, bad uta u jingthaw basaw u kum ka pukni baher.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad kita ki saw ki jingthaw ba-im ki da don uwei pa uwei, hynriew ki thapniang, baroh sawdong bad shapoh ki da dap da ki khmat, bad kim ïoh kaba shongthait mynsngi bad mynmiet, ki da ong, “U Bakhuid, U Bakhuid, U Bakhuid, U Trai uba U Blei Badonbor baroh, uta uba la ju long bad uta uba long bad uta u ban sa wan.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad haba kita ki jingthaw ba-im ki ïa-ai ka burom bad ka jingpyndonburom bad ka jingnguh ha uta uba shong halor kata ka khet, ha uta u ba-im sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> kita ki arphew saw ngut ki tymmen basan ki ïahap dem ha khmat uta uba shong halor kata ka khet, bad ki ïamane ïa uta u ba-im sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut, bad ki ïabred ïa kita ki pansngiat jong ki ha khmat kata ka khet, ki da ong,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Me long uba dei, A Trai bad U Blei jong ngi, ban pdiang ïa kata ka burom bad ïa kata ka jingpyndonburom bad ïa kata ka bor, naba me la thaw ma me ïa kiei kiei baroh, bad namar kata ka mon jong me ki ïalong, bad la thaw ïa ki.”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ha ka kti kamon jong uta uba shong halor kata ka khet ïa ka kitab, ïa kaba la thoh shapoh bad shalor, ïa kaba la pyndait laha da ki hynñiew ki jingpyndait.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa u angel u bakhlaiñ, u da pyrta da ka ktien bajam, “Uei uba bit ban plied ïa kata ka kitab, bad ban loit ïa ki jingpyndait jong ka?”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ym don ha bneng, lymne ha ka khyndew, lymne shapoh ka khyndew, uba lah ban plied ïa kata ka kitab, lymne wat ban khmih ha ka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nga te, nga la ïam shibun, naba ym shym la shem ïano ïano ruh uba bit ban plied ïa kata ka kitab, lymne wat ban khmih ha ka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te uwei na kita ki tymmen basan u ong ha nga, “To wat ïam: ha khmih, uta U Sing uba long na ka jaid Judah, U Thied u Dabid, u la jop ban plied ïa kata ka kitab, bad ban loit ïa kita ki hynñiew ki jingpyndait jong ka.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad nga la ïohi hapdeng kata ka khet bad kita ki saw ki jingthaw ba-im, bad hapdeng kita ki tymmen basan, ïa U Khun langbrot u da ïeng, kum ïa uba la pynïap, u da don hynñiew ki reng, bad hynñiew ki khmat, kiba long kita ki hynñiew ki mynsiem U Blei, ïa kiba la phah noh sha ka pyrthei baroh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la leit, bad u la shim ïa kata ka kitab na ka kti kamon jong uta uba shong halor kata ka khet.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te mynba u la shim ïa kata ka kitab, kita ki saw ki jingthaw ba-im bad kita ki arphew saw ngut ki tymmen basan ki la ïahap dem ha khmat uta U Khun langbrot, ki da don uwei pa uwei la ka duitara, bad ki pliang ksiar ba dap da ki jingainguh thang baiwbih, kiba long ki jingduwai jong ki riewkhuid.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki ïarwai ïa ka jingrwai bathymmai, ki da ong, “Me long uba dei ban shim ïa kata ka kitab, bad ban plie ïa kita ki jingpyndait jong ka; naba la pynïap keiñ ïa me, bad me la siewspah ha U Blei da ka snam jong me ïa kiba na ka jaid, bad na ka thylliej, bad na u paidlang, bad na ka kynja bynriew baroh;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad me la pynlong ïa ki, ki syiem bad ki lyngdoh ha U Blei jong ngi, bad kin ïasynshar ha ka pyrthei.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te nga la ïohi, bad nga la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien sawa shibun ki angel baroh sawdong kata ka khet bad kita ki jingthaw ba-im bad kita ki tymmen basan ruh; bad ka jingkheiñ ïa ki, ka la long ki shiphew hajar sien ki shiphew hajar, bad ki hajar sien ki hajar,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ki da ong da ka ktien bajam, “U long uba dei uta U Khun langbrot, ïa uba la pynïap, ban ïoh pdiang ïa kata ka bor, bad ïa ka jingkynrei spah, bad ïa ka jingstad, bad ïa ka jinglah, bad ïa ka jingpyndonburom bad ïa ka burom, bad ïa ka jingkyrkhu.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ïa ka jingthaw baroh kaba don ha bneng, bad halor ka khyndew, bad shapoh ka khyndew, bad ha ka duriaw, bad kiei kiei baroh kiba ha kita, nga la ïohsngew haba ki ong, “Ha uta uba shong halor kata ka khet, bad ha uta U Khun langbrot, to long ka jingkyrkhu, bad ka jingpyndonburom, bad ka burom, bad ka bor, sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut!”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad kita ki saw ki jingthaw ba-im ki la ïa-ong, “Amen”. Bad kita ki arphew saw ngut ki tymmen basan ki la ïahap dem, bad ki la ïamane."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad nga la khmih mynba uta U Khun langbrot u la plie ïa kawei na kita ki hynñiew ki jingpyndait, bad nga la ïohsngew ïa uwei na kita ki saw tylli ki jingthaw ba-im ba u da kren kum ka jingriew u pyrthat, “To ale, bad to khmih.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te nga la khmih keiñ, bad ha khmih, ka kulai balieh, bad uta uba shong halor jong ka u la don ka ryntieh; bad la ai ha u ïa ka pansngiat, bad u la leit mih noh da kaba jop thiaw, bad ïa ka ban jop thiaw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad mynba u la plie ïa ka jingpyndait ka ba-ar, nga la ïohsngew ïa uta u jingthaw ba-im u ba-ar ba u ong, “To ale, bad to khmih.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ka la leit mih noh kawei pat ka kulai basaw: bad ha uta uba shong halor jong ka, la ai bor ban shim noh ïa ka jingsuk na kata ka khyndew, khnang ba kin da ïoh ïa-pynïap noh paralok hi; te la ai ha u ka waitlam bakhraw.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad mynba u la plie ïa ka jingpyndait ka balai, nga la ïohsngew ïa uta u jingthaw ba-im u balai ba u ong, “To ale, bad to khmih.” Te nga la khmih, bad ha khmih, ka kulai baïong; bad uta uba shong halor jong ka u da bat ïa ka tarajur ha ka kti jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien hapdeng kita ki jingthaw ba-im, kaba ong, “Ka shi ser u Kew ïa ka shi suka, bad lai ser u Kew Barli ïa ka shi suka; bad to me wat pynsniew ïa ka umphniang bad ïa ka Waiñ!”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad mynba u la plie ïa ka jingpyndait ka basaw, nga la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien jong uta u jingthaw ba-im u basaw, ka da ong, “To ale, bad to khmih.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te nga la khmih, bad ha khmih ka kulai balieh bthuh, bad uta uba shong halor jong ka uba kyrteng “u Jingïap”; bad kata ka Jaka shong riewïap ka bud lem bad u. Bad la ai ka bor ha ki, halor ka shi pawa kata ka khyndew, ban pynïap noh da ka waitlam, bad da ka 'nemsniew, bad da ka jingïapthem, bad da kita ki mrad khlaw jong kata ka khyndew.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad mynba u la plie ïa ka jingpyndait ka basan, nga la ïohi hapoh ka duwan ïa ki mynsiem ki jong kita ïa kiba la pynïap noh na ka bynta ka ktien U Blei, bad na ka bynta kata ka jingphla ïa kaba ki la ju ïabat skhem.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ki la pyrta da ka ktien bajam, ki da ïa-ong, “Tad lano, ko Trai Kynrad, U Bakhuid bad U Bashisha, mem bishar kut bad pynhiar kput na ka bynta kata ka snam jong ngi halor kita kiba shong ha kata ka khyndew?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad la ai ha uwei pa uwei baroh ïa ka jaiñkup balieh; bad la ong ha ki, ba kin da ïashong thait shuh sa shibit ar bit, tad ynda yn pyndep noh ïa kita ki para shakri jong ki ruh bad kita ki parabangeit jong ki, ïa ki ban sa pynïap noh kumba ïa ki ruh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad nga la ïohi mynba u la plie ïa ka jingpyndait ka bahynriew, bad la long ka jingkhynñiuh jumai bakhraw; bad ka sngi ka la kylla ïong kum ka jaiñ shñiuh bakhain, bad u bnai pyllun u la kylla kum ka snam;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ki khlur ka bneng ki la hap sha ka khyndew, kumba ki khlur noh ki soh ki bym-ih na u dieng Dumbur, haba la pynkhih ïa u da ka lyer bakhraw.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ïa ka bneng la pynkynran noh kum ka kitab haba la kli noh; bad ïa u lum bad ka 'dewlynnong baroh la pynkynriah noh na ki jaka jong ki.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te kita ki syiem jong ka khyndew, bad kita ki bakhraw batri, bad kita ki rangbah shihajar, bad kita ki bariewspah, bad kita ki bakhlaiñ, bad u mraw baroh bad uba laitluid baroh, ki la ïabuhrieh ïa lade ha ki krem bad hapdeng ki mawsiang jong ki lum bah;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ki ïa-ong ha kita ki lum bah bad ha kita ki mawsiang, “To hap ha ngi, bad to buhrieh noh ïa ngi na ka khmat uta u bashong halor kata ka khet, bad na ka jingbitar jong uta U Khun langbrot;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> naba kata ka sngi kaba khraw ka jingbitar jong u ka la wan keiñ; te uei uba lah ban ïeng?”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hadien kane, nga la ïohi ïa ki saw ki angel kiba ïeng halor ki sawdong ka khyndew, ba ki ïabat ïa ki saw lyer ka khyndew, khnang ba ka lyer kan ym ïoh beh ha ka khyndew, lymne ha ka duriaw, lymne ha kano kano ka dieng.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa uwei pat u angel ba u wan kiew na sha ba-mih ka sngi, u da bat ïa ka shab jong U Blei U Ba-im; bad u la pyrta da ka ktien bajam ha kita ki saw angel, ha kiba la ai bor ban pynsniew ïa ka khyndew bad ïa ka duriaw,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> u da ong, “To wat pynsniew ïa ka khyndew, lymne ïa ka duriaw, lymne ïa ki dieng, ha ban da ngi la ïoh shon ïa ki shakri U Blei jong ngi halor ki shyllangmat jong ki.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew ïa ka jingkheiñ jong kita ïa kiba la shon, shispah sawphew saw hajar, ïa kiba la shon na ka jaid baroh ki khun Israel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ka jaid Judah la shon khat-ar hajar; Na ka jaid Reuben khat-ar hajar; Na ka jaid Gad khat-ar hajar;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ka jaid Asher khat-ar hajar; Na ka jaid Naphtali khat-ar hajar; Na ka jaid Manasseh khat-ar hajar;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ka jaid Simeon khat-ar hajar; Na ka jaid Lebi khat-ar hajar; Na ka jaid Issakhar khat-ar hajar;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ka jaid Sabulon khat-ar hajar; Na ka jaid Joseph khat-ar hajar; Na ka jaid Benjamin la shon khat-ar hajar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, nga la khmih, bad ha khmih, u paidbah byllien, ïa uba uno uno um lah ban ñiew, na ki kynja bynriew bad na ki jaid bad na ki paidlang bad na ki thylliej baroh, ba ki da ïeng ha khmat kata ka khet bad ha khmat uta U Khun langbrot, kiba la kup ki jaiñkup balieh, bad ki dieng Tlai ha ki kti jong ki;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ki da ïapyrta da ka ktien bajam, ki da ïa-ong, “Ka jingpynim ha U Blei jong ngi uba shong halor kata ka khet, bad ha uta U Khun langbrot!”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad kita ki angel baroh ki la ïaïeng tawiar ïa kata ka khet bad ïa kita ki tymmen basan bad ïa kita ki saw ki jingthaw ba-im, bad ki la ïahap dem la ki khmat ha khmat kata ka khet, bad ki la ïamane dem ïa U Blei,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ki da ïa-ong: “Amen! Ka jingkyrkhu bad ka burom bad ka jingstad bad ka jingainguh bad ka jingpyndonburom bad ka bor bad ka jinglah ha U Blei jong ngi sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut: Amen.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te uwei na kita ki tymmen basan u la kylli, u da ong ha nga, “Kine kiba la kup kita ki jaiñkup balieh, hato ki long kiei bad nangno ki la wan?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te nga la ïathuh ha u, “Ko Kynrad, me tip ma me.” Te u la ong ha nga, “Kine ki long kita keiñ kiba wan na kata ka jingjynjar bakhraw, bad ki la sait ïa kita ki jaiñkup jong ki, bad ki la pynkhuid lieh ïa ki ha ka snam jong uta U Khun langbrot.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Namar kata, ki long ha khmat kata ka khet U Blei, bad ki ïashakri ïa u mynsngi bad mynmiet ha ka jaka kyntang jong u; bad uta uba shong halor kata ka khet un shongkah halor jong ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kin ym thngan shuh, lymne sliang shuh, lymne ka sngi kan ym ïoh shoh ha ki, lymne kano kano ka jingshit;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> naba uta U Khun langbrot uba hapdeng kata ka khet un sharai ïa ki, bad un ïalam lynti ïa ki sha ki pukri um ka jingim; bad U Blei un ñiad noh ïa ka jingjaw ummat baroh na ki khmat jong ki.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad mynba u la plie ïa ka jingpyndait ka bahynñiew, ka la long ka jingsngap jar ha bneng kumba shiteng kynta.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa ki hynñiew ki angel kiba ïeng ha khmat U Blei, bad ha ki, la ai hynñiew ki turoi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te uwei pat u angel u la wan bad u la ïeng hajan ka duwan, u da don ka pliang ksiar bathang iwbih; bad la ai ha u shibun ka jingainguh thang baiwbih, ba un ïoh pynlang ïa ka ha ki jingduwai ki riewkhuid baroh halor kata ka duwan ksiar kaba ha khmat kata ka khet.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ka tdem kita ki jingainguh thang baiwbih lem bad kita ki jingduwai jong ki riewkhuid, ka la leit kiew ha khmat U Blei na ka kti uta u angel.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad uta u angel u la shim ïa kata ka pliang bathang iwbih, bad u la pyndap ïa ka da ka ding na kata ka duwan, bad u la bred ïa ka shalor ka khyndew; te la long ki pyrthat bad ki jingsawa bad ki leilieh, bad ka jingkhynñiuh jumai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad kita ki hynñiew ki angel kiba don kita ki hynñiew ki turoi ki la ïakhreh ïa lade ban pynsawa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te uta u banyngkong u la pynsawa; bad la jia long u phria bad ka ding ïa kiba la khleh da ka snam, bad la bred ïa ki shalor ka khyndew; te ïa ka balai ka bynta na ka jong ka khyndew bad ïa ka balai ka bynta na ka jong ki dieng la thang noh, bad ïa u phlang bajyrngam baroh la thang noh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u angel u ba-ar u la pynsawa; te kum ïa u lum bakhraw ïa uba la thang da ka ding la bred sha ka duriaw; te ka balai ka bynta na ka jong kata ka duriaw ka la kylla snam,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad la ïap noh ka balai ka bynta na ka jong kita ki jingthaw kiba ha kata ka duriaw, kiba don jingim, bad la pynjot noh ïa ka balai ka bynta na ka jong ki lieng.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u angel u balai u la pynsawa; te la hap na bneng u khlur bakhraw bathang kum ka musa, bad u la hap halor ka balai ka bynta na ka jong ki wah bad halor ki pukri ki um;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad ka kyrteng uta u khlur la khot “U Bakthang”; te ka balai ka bynta na ka jong kita ki um ka la kylla kthang; te shibun ki briew ki la ïap noh na kita ki um, naba la pynkthang ïa ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u angel u basaw u la pynsawa; te la shoh ïa ka balai ka bynta na ka jong ka sngi, bad ïa ka balai ka bynta na ka jong u bnai, bad ïa ka balai ka bynta na ka jong ki khlur, khnang ban pyndum ïa kata ka balai ka bynta jong ki, bad kata ka sngi kam pynshai ïa kata ka balai ka bynta jong ka, bad ka miet kumjuh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad nga la khmih, bad nga la ïohsngew ïa uwei u pukni uba her hapdeng ka bneng, u da ong da ka ktien kaba jam, “Kordit, kordit, kordit, ha kita kiba shong halor kata ka khyndew, namar kita kiwei pat ki jingsawa ka turoi jong kita ki lai angel ki ban sa pynsawa!”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u angel u basan u la pynsawa; te nga la ïohi ïa u khlur ba la hap na bneng sha ka khyndew; bad la ai ha u ïa u shabi kata ka 'liewlong kaba khlem trai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u la plie ïa kata ka 'liewlong bakhlem trai; te ka la leit kiew ka tdem na kata ka 'liewlong, kum ka tdem ka lawar ding kaba khraw; te la pyndum ïa ka sngi bad ïa ka suiñbneng da ka tdem jong kata ka 'liewlong.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad na kata ka tdem la mih noh ki puit halor ka khyndew; bad ha ki, la ai ka bor, kumba ki 'ñianglartham jong ka khyndew ki don ka bor.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad la ong ha ki ba kin ym pynsniew ïa u phlang ka khyndew, lymne ïa kaei kaei ruh ka bajyrngam, lymne ïa uno uno ruh u dieng, hynrei, tang ïa kita ki briew ki bymdon kata ka jingshon shab jong U Blei halor ki shyllangmat jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad la ai ha ki ba kin ym pynïap noh ïa ki, hynrei, ba yn pynkordit ïa ki, san bnai: te kata ka jingpynkordit ïa ki, ka la long kum ka jingpynkordit ka 'ñianglartham haba ka la dait ïa u briew.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ha kita ki sngi, ki briew kin wad noh ïa ka jingïap, bad kin ym shem ïa ka satia; bad kin kwah eh ban ïap noh, te kata ka jingïap kan phet noh na ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki dur kita ki puit ki la syriem kum ki kulai ïa kiba la khreh ïa ka thma; bad halor ki khlieh jong ki, ki la don kum ki pansngiat kiba syriem ïa ka ksiar, bad ki khmat jong ki kum ki khmat ki briew,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad ki la don u shñiuh kum u shñiuh ki kynthei, bad ki bniat jong ki, ki la long kum ki jong ki sing;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> bad ki la don ki jingïada shadem kum ki jingïada shadem nar; bad ka jingsawa ki thapniang jong ki, ka kum ka jingsawa ki kali babun ki kulai haba ki ïatur keiñ sha ka thma;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ki don ki tdong kiba syriem ïa ki 'ñianglartham, bad ki sni; bad ka bor jong ki ban pynsniew ïa ki briew san bnai ka la long ha ki tdong jong ki.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki don u syiem halor jong ki, uba u angel kata ka 'liewlong bakhlem trai, uba ka kyrteng jong u ha ka Hebru ka long “u Abaddon”, bad ha ka Grik u don ka kyrteng “u Apollion”.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kata kawei ka jingpynkordit ka la dep noh: ha khmih, ki dang wan shuh sa ar ki jingpynkordit hadien.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u angel u bahynriew u la pynsawa; te nga la ïohsngew ïa kawei ka ktien sawa na kita ki reng jong kata ka duwan ksiar kaba ha khmat U Blei,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> ka da ong ha uta u angel u bahynriew uba la don kata ka turoi, “To pyllait noh ïa kita ki saw angel ïa kiba la khum hajan kata ka wah ka bakhraw ‘ka Ïuphratis’.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te la pyllait noh ïa kita ki saw ngut ki angel, ïa kiba la khreh khnang ïa kata ka por bad ïa ka sngi bad ïa u bnai bad ïa ka snem, ba kin ïoh pynïap noh ïa ka balai ka bynta jong ki briew.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ka jingkheiñ ki paidïapom shong kulai ki la long ki arspah hajar ki hajar: nga la ïohsngew keiñ ïa kata ka jingkheiñ jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te kumne nga la ïohi ïa kita ki kulai ha kata ka jingithuhpaw, bad ïa kita kiba shong halor jong ki, kiba don ki jingïada shadem kum ka ding, bad kum ki Haïakinth, bad kum u kyndok; bad ki khlieh kita ki kulai, ki kum ki khlieh ki sing; bad na ki shyntur jong ki, ka mih ka ding bad ka tdem bad u kyndok.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Da kine lai tylli ki jingïapthem la pynïap noh ïa kata ka balai ka bynta jong ki briew, da kata ka ding, bad da kata ka tdem, bad da uta u kyndok, kiba la mih noh na kita ki shyntur jong ki.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Naba kata ka bor jong kita ki kulai ka long ha ka shyntur jong ki, bad ha ki tdong jong ki; namar kita ki tdong jong ki, ki syriem kum ki bseiñ, bad ki don ki khlieh, bad da kita, ki pynsniew.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te kita kiba sah na ki bynriew, ïa kiba ym shym la pynïap noh da kine ki jingïapthem, kim shym la kylla-ka-bamut na kita ki jingleh ki kti jong ki, ba kin ym mane ïa kita ki ksuid, bad ïa kita ki bleithaw kiba da ka ksiar, bad da ka rupa, bad da ka rnong, bad da u maw, bad da ka dieng, ki bym lah ban ïohi, lymne ïohsngew, lymne ïaid:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad kim shym la kylla-ka-bamut na kita ki jingpynïap jong ki, lymne na kata kaba ai ksuid jong ki, lymne na kata ka jingïakai kynthei jong ki, lymne na kita ki jingtuh jong ki."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa uwei pat u angel bakhrawbor ba u wan hiar na bneng, uba la kup da u lyoh; bad u simpyllieng halor ka khlieh jong u, bad ka khmat jong u ka la kum ka sngi, bad ki kjat jong u, kum ki rijied ding;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u don ha ka kti jong u ka kitab rit ba la plie. Bad u la buh ïa ka kjat kamon jong u halor ka duriaw, bad ïa kadiang halor ka khyndew;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad u la pyrta da ka ktien bajam, kumba kyrhuh u sing; te mynba u la pyrta, ki hynñiew ki pyrthat ki la ïalap ïa ki ktien sawa jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te mynba kita ki hynñiew ki pyrthat ki la ïalap, nga la sa ba ngan sa thoh; hynrei, nga la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien na bneng kaba ong ha nga, “To pyndait laha ïa kita kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba kita ki hynñiew ki pyrthat ki la ïalap, bad to wat thoh ïa kita kiei kiei ruh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te uta u angel ïa uba nga la ïohi ba u da ïeng halor kata ka duriaw bad halor kata ka khyndew, u la rah ïa la ka kti kamon sha bneng,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u la smai ha uta uba ïai-im sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut, uba la thaw ïa ka bneng bad kiei kiei ruh kiba ha ka, bad ïa ka khyndew bad kiei kiei ruh kiba ha ka, bad ïa ka duriaw bad kiei kiei ruh kiba ha ka, ba kan ym long ka jingpyntud shuh:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> hynrei, ha kita ki sngi, kata ka ktien sawa ka jong uta u angel u bahynñiew, hamar ba un sa pynsawa, hangta la pyndep noh ïa kata ka jingmaïan ka jong U Blei, kumba u la ïathuhkhana babha ha kita ki shakri jong u ki nongïathuhlypa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kata ka ktien ïa kaba nga la ïohsngew na bneng ka la kren pat bad nga, bad ka la ong, “To khie leit, to shim ïa kata ka kitab rit ba la plie ha ka kti uta u angel uba ïeng halor kata ka duriaw bad halor kata ka khyndew.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te nga la leit sha uta u angel, nga da ong ha u, “To ai noh ha nga ïa kata ka kitab rit.” Te u la ong ha nga, “To shim bad to bam duh ïa ka; te kan pynkthang ïa ka kpoh jong me, hynrei, ha ka shyntur jong me kan long kaba thiang kum ka ngap;”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te nga la shim ïa kata ka kitab rit na ka kti uta u angel, bad nga la bam duh ïa ka; te ka la long ha ka shyntur jong nga kaba thiang kum ka ngap; te haba nga la bam ïa ka, la pynkthang noh ïa ka kpoh jong nga.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u la ong ha nga, “Ka dei ïa me ban ïathuhlypa pat shaphang shibun ki paidlang, bad ki kynja bynriew, bad ki thylliej, bad ki syiem.”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad la ai ha nga ïa u stew basyriem kum u dieng; bad don uba la ong, “To ïeng, bad to thew ïa ka templ U Blei, bad ïa ka duwan, bad ïa kita kiba ïamane ha ka;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> hynrei, ïa ka phyllaw kaba shabar kata ka templ U Blei men iehnoh noh, men ym thew ïa ka; naba la ai noh ïa ka ha ki Jentil: bad ïa ka nongbah ka bakhuid kin ïaïuh top jin sawphew ar bnai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ngan ai bor ha ki ar ngut ki nongïaphla jong nga, te kin ïathuhlypa shi hajar arspah hynriewphew sngi, kiba la kup ki jaiñ khain.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kine ki long kita ki ar tylli ki dieng Olib bad kita ki ar tylli ki dieng pynïeng sharak, kiba ïeng ha khmat U Trai jong ka khyndew.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad lada uno uno ruh u kwah ban pynsniew ïa ki ka ding ka mih noh na ka shyntur jong ki, bad ka bam duh ïa ki nongshun jong ki: te lada uno uno ruh u kwah ban pynsniew ïa ki, kumjuh ka dei ban pynïap noh ïa uta.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kine ki don ka bor ban khang khop ïa ka bneng, ba u slap un ym hap ha ki sngi kata ka jingïathuhlypa jong ki: bad ki don ka bor halor ki um ban pynkylla snam ïa ki, bad ban shoh ïa ka khyndew da ki jingïapthem baroh katno katno sien ruh katba ki ïakwah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ynda ki la ïoh pyndep noh ïa kata ka jingphla jong ki, uta u mrad uba kiew noh na kata ka 'liewlong bakhlem trai, un pynlong ïa ka jingïaleh thma bad ki, bad un jop thiaw ïa ki, bad un pynïap noh ïa ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki metïap jong ki kin shu sah ha ka lynti bah kata ka shnong ka bakhraw, ïa kaba la khot ha ka jingmut bakynja mynsiem, “ka Sodom” bad “ka Ijipt”; hangta ruh, la sahnarphna ïa U Trai jong ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te kiba na kita ki paidlang bad ki jaid bad ki thylliej bad ki kynja bynriew kin ïakhmih ïa kita ki metïap jong ki, lai sngi shiteng, bad kin ym shah ban buh ïa kita ki metïap jong ki ha ki jingtep.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad kita kiba ïashong halor kata ka khyndew kin ïakmen halor jong ki, bad kin ïaleh biria, bad kin ïaphah lam ïa ki jingai sngewbha paralok hi; naba kine ki ar ngut ki nongïathuhlypa ki la ïapynkordit ïa kita kiba ïashong halor ka khyndew.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te hadien kita ki lai sngi shiteng, U Mynsiem ka jingim na U Blei u la leit bsut ha ki, bad ki la ïeng joit da ki kjat jong ki; te ka jingsheptieng bakhraw ka la ngat ha kita kiba la khmih ïa ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien bajam na bneng kaba ong ha ki, “To wan kiew shane.” Te ki la ïaleit kiew noh sha bneng ha u lyoh; bad kita ki nongshun jong ki, ki la ïakhmih ïa ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ha kata kajuh ka por ka la long ka jingkhynñiuh jumai bakhraw, te kaba shiphew ka bynta na kata ka nongbah ka la kyllon khram; bad la pynïap noh ha kata ka jingkhynñiuh jumai hynñiew hajar ki briew: te kita kiba sah ki la ïasheptieng eh, bad ki la ïa-ai burom ha U Blei ka bneng.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kata ka jingpynkordit ka ba-ar ka la wai noh: ha khmih kata ka jingpynkordit ka balai ka wan kloi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u angel u bahynñiew u la pynsawa; bad ki la long ki ktien bajam ha bneng kiba ong, “Kata ka hima ka jong ka pyrthei ka la jia long ka jong U Trai jong ngi, bad U Khrist jong u: te un synshar keiñ sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad kita ki arphew saw ngut ki tymmen basan, kiba shong ha khmat U Blei halor ki khet jong ki, ki la dem da pyllup bad ki la ïamane dem ïa U Blei,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ki da ong, “Ngi ïanguh ïa me, ko Trai uba U Blei Badonbor Baroh, uba long bad uba la ju long; naba me la shimti ïa la ka bor kaba khraw, bad me la synshar.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ki la khih bitar lep kita ki kynja bynriew, bad kata ka jingbitar jong me ka la jia, bad kata ka Ïa ban bishar ïa ki nongïap, bad ban ai ïa ka nong ha ki shakri jong me, kita ki nongïathuhlypa, bad ha kita ki riewkhuid, bad ha kita kiba sheptieng ïa ka kyrteng jong me, ki barit baraiñ bad ki bakhraw batri; bad ban pynjot noh ïa kita kiba pynjot noh ïa ka pyrthei.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te la plie ïa ka templ U Blei ha bneng; bad la ïohi ïa ka synduk ka jutang jong u ha kata ka templ jong u; bad la don ki leilieh, bad ki jingsawa, bad ki pyrthat, bad ka jingkhynñiuh jumai, bad u phria bakhraw."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad la ïohi ïa ka dak khyllah bakhraw ha bneng; ka briew kaba la kup da ka sngi, bad u bnai hapoh ki kjat jong ka, bad halor ka khlieh jong ka, ka pansngiat da ki khat-ar ki khlur;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ka la punkhun, bad ka kyang jam haba ka suhkhun, bad haba ka pang shitom ban kha khun.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad la ïohi ïa kawei pat ka dak khyllah ha bneng; bad ha khmih, u ïakjakor basaw uba khraw, uba don hynñiew ki khlieh bad shiphew ki reng, bad halor kita ki khlieh jong u, hynñiew ki pansngiat.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ka tdong jong u ka ring ïa ka balai ka bynta na ki khlur ka bneng, bad ka la bred noh ïa ki sha ka khyndew: bad uta u ïakjakor u la ïeng ha khmat kata ka briew ka ban sa kha khun, khnang ba ynda ka la kha, un ïoh bam duh ïa ita i khunlung jong ka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ka la kha ïa u khun shynrang, u ban sa synshar ïa ki kynja bynriew baroh da ka dieng synshar nar; te la rong noh artet ïa ita i khunlung jong ka sha U Blei, bad sha ka khet jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad kata ka briew ka la phet ïap sha ka ri khlaw, ha kaba ka don ka jaka ïa kaba la khreh da U Blei, khnang ba hangta kin ïoh ïabsa ïa ka, shi hajar arspah hynriewphew sngi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ka thma ka la long ha bneng: u Mikhal bad ki angel jong u ki la ïaleh thma ïa uta u ïakjakor; te uta u ïakjakor ruh bad ki angel jong u ki la ïaleh thma;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> hynrei, kim shym la jop, lymne ïa ka jaka jong ki ym shym la shem shuh ha bneng.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te la shop noh arsut ïa uta u ïakjakor bakhraw, uta u bseiñ tymmen ïa uba la khot “u Ksuid”, bad “u Soitan”, uba shukor ïa ka pyrthei baroh kawei; la shop noh arsut ïa u sha ka khyndew, bad ïa kita ki angel jong u la shop noh arsut lem bad u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien bajam ha bneng, kaba ong, “Mynta la wan jia kata ka jingpynim bad kata ka bor, bad kata ka hima U Blei jong ngi bad kata ka bor synshar uta U Khrist jong u: naba la shop noh arsut ïa uta u nongmudui ïa ki parabangeit jong ngi, uba shait mudui ïa ki ha khmat U Blei jong ngi mynsngi bad mynmiet.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, ki la jop noh ma ki ïa u, namar kata ka snam jong uta u Khun langbrot, bad namar kata ka ktien ka jingphla jong ki; te kim shym la ieit ïa ka jingim jong ki jin haduh ka jingïap.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Naba kumta to ïakmen, ko ki bneng, bad phi kiba shong ha ki. Kordit ïa kata ka khyndew, bad ïa ka duriaw! naba uta u Ksuid u la leit hiar ha phi, uba don ka jingbitar bakhraw, naba u tip ba u don tang khyndiat por.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te mynba uta u ïakjakor u la ïohi ba la shop noh arsut ïa u sha ka khyndew, u la behbeiñ ïa kata ka briew kaba la kha khun shynrang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te la ai ha kata ka briew ar tylli ki thapniang jong ka pukni ka bakhraw, ba kan da ïoh her noh sha kata ka ri khlaw sha kata ka jaka jong ka, ha kaba yn bsa ïa ka shi Ïa, bad ki Ïa, bad ka shiteng Ïa, na khmat uta u bseiñ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad uta u bseiñ u la theh buk buk na ka shyntur jong u ïa ka um kum ka wah na shadien kata ka briew, khnang ba un ïoh pynrong noh ïa ka da kata ka wah.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, kata ka khyndew ka la ïarap ïa kata ka briew, te kata ka khyndew ka la ang ïa la ka shyntur, bad ka la nguid noh khoit ïa kata ka wah ïa kaba uta u ïakjakor u la theh buk buk na ka shyntur jong u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te uta u ïakjakor u la sngewbitar lep ïa kata ka briew, bad u la leit noh ban ïaleh thma bad kita kiba sah na u symbai jong ka, kita kiba sumar ïa ki hukum U Blei bad kiba bat ïa kata ka jingphla ïa U Jisu Khrist. Te u la ïeng halor u shyiap ka duriaw."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa u mrad khlaw uba kiew noh na ka duriaw, uba don hynñiew ki khlieh bad shiphew ki reng, bad halor kita ki reng jong u, shiphew ki pansngiat, bad halor kita ki khlieh jong u ki kyrteng ka jingkrenbeiñ Blei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad uta u mrad khlaw ïa uba nga la ïohi, u la syriem ïa u 'labasa, bad ki kjat jong u kum ki kjat dngiem, bad ka shyntur jong u kum ka shyntur sing: te uta u ïakjakor u la aiti ha u ïa ka bor jong u, bad ïa ka khet jong u, bad ïa ka bor synshar bakhraw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa kawei na kita ki khlieh jong u kum ïa kaba la pynmong haduh ka ban ïap; hynrei, la pynkhiah ïa kata ka jingmong ïap jong u: te baroh kawei ka pyrthei ka la sngewphylla ïa uta u mrad khlaw.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki la ïamane dem ïa uta u ïakjakor naba u la aiti ïa ka bor synshar jong u ha uta u mrad khlaw; te ki la ïamane dem ïa uta u mrad khlaw, ki da ong, “Uei, uba long kum uta u mrad khlaw? uei uba lah ban ïaleh thma bad u?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te la ai ha u ka shyntur kaba ïalap ïa kiei kiei ki bakhraw, bad ïa ki jingkrenbeiñ Blei; bad la ai ha u ïa ka bor synshar ban sah jin sawphew ar bnai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u la ang ïa ka shyntur jong u ïa ka ban krenbeiñ ïa U Blei, ban krenbeiñ ïa ka kyrteng jong u, bad ïa ka ïing kyntang jong u, bad ïa kita kiba shong ha bneng.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad la ai bor ha u ban ïaleh thma bad kita ki riewkhuid, bad ban jop noh ïa ki: bad la ai ha u ïa ka bor synshar halor ka jaid, bad u paidlang, bad ka thylliej, bad ka kynja bynriew baroh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kita baroh kiba shong halor ka khyndew kin ïamane dem ïa u, kiba ki kyrteng jong ki ym shym la thoh ha kata ka kitab ka jingim jong uta U Khun langbrot, ïa uba la pynïap la myndanglong ka pyrthei.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Lada uno uno ruh u don ka shkor, to un sngew.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Lada uno uno ruh u ïalam mraw, u leit noh hi keiñ sha ka jinglongmraw: lada uno uno ruh u pynïap noh da ka waitlam, ka dei ban pynïap noh ïa u da ka waitlam. “Hangne don ka jingïaishah bad ka jingngeit jong kita ki riewkhuid.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa uwei pat u mrad khlaw uba kiew noh na kata ka khyndew; bad u la don ar tylli ki reng ba syriem kum i khun langbrot, bad u la kren kum u ïakjakor.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ïa kata ka bor synshar baroh ka jong uta u mrad khlaw banyngkong u leh ha khmat jong u, bad u pynbor ïa kata ka khyndew bad ïa kita kiba shong ha ka ba kin ïamane dem ïa uta u mrad khlaw banyngkong, ïa uba la pynkhiah ïa kata ka jingmong ïap jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u leh ïa ki dak khyllah bakhraw, kat ban pynhiar ïa ka ding na bneng sha ka khyndew ha khmat ki briew.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u shukor noh ïa kita kiba shong halor kata ka khyndew, da kita ki dak khyllah ïa kiba la ai bor ha u ban leh ha khmat uta u mrad khlaw; u da ong ha kita kiba shong halor kata ka khyndew ba kin thaw dur ïa uta u mrad khlaw, uba la ïoh ïa kata ka jingmong da ka waitlam, bad ba la ïoh im pynban.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad la ai bor ha u ban ai ka mynsiem ha kata ka dur uta u mrad khlaw, ba kata ka dur uta u mrad khlaw kan da ïoh kren ruh, bad ba kan ïoh pynlong ba kat ki ban ym mane dem ïa kata ka dur uta u mrad khlaw, yn pynïap noh ïa ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u pynlong ïa ki baroh, ïa ki barit baraiñ ruh bad ki bakhraw batri, ïa ki bariewspah ruh bad ki baduk, ïa kiba laitluid ruh bad ki mraw, ba yn buh ha ki, ïa ka dak halor ka kti kamon jong ki, lane halor ki shyllangmat jong ki;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> bad ba uno uno ruh un ym lah ban thied lane ban die, hynrei, tang uta uba don kata ka dak, kata ka kyrteng hi uta u mrad khlaw keiñ, lane kata ka jingkheiñ ka kyrteng jong u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hangne don ka jingstad. Uta uba don ka jingshemphang, to un kheiñ ïa kata ka jingkheiñ uta u mrad khlaw; namar ka long ka jingkheiñ u briew: bad kata ka jingkheiñ jong u ka long, Hynriewspah hynriewphew hynriew."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te nga la ïohi, bad ha khmih, U Khun langbrot u ïeng halor u lum Seïon, bad lem bad u ruh shispah sawphew saw hajar ngut, kiba don kata ka kyrteng jong u, bad ka kyrteng U Kpa jong u, ïa kaba la thoh halor ki shyllangmat jong ki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien sawa na bneng, kum ka jingsawa shibun ki um, bad kum ka jingsawa u pyrthat bakhraw: bad kata ka jingsawa kaba nga la ïohsngew, ka la long kum ka jingsawa ki nongtem duitara haba ki ïatem ha ki duitara jong ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki ïarwai kum ïa ka jingrwai bathymmai ha khmat kata ka khet, bad ha khmat kita ki saw ki jingthaw ba-im bad kita ki tymmen basan; bad uno uno ruh um lah ban nang keiñ ïa kata ka jingrwai, hynrei, tang kita ki shispah sawphew saw hajar, kita keiñ ïa kiba la siewspah noh na ka khyndew.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kine ki long kita ïa kiba ym shym la pynbit-tngit bad ki kynthei, namar ki long ki rangsotti. Kine ki long kita kiba bud ïa uta U Khun langbrot kat shaba u leit. Ïa kine la siewspah noh napdeng ki briew, kum u soh nyngkong ha U Blei bad ha uta U Khun langbrot.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ha ka shyntur jong ki ym shym la shem ïa kaba arsap; ki long kiba khlem pop.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa uwei pat u angel uba her hapdeng ka bneng, uba don ka gospel bymjukut ban ïathuhkhana ha kita kiba shong halor kata ka khyndew, bad ha ka kynja bynriew bad ka jaid bad ka thylliej bad u paidlang baroh;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad u ong da ka ktien bajam, “To sheptieng ïa U Blei, bad to ai ka burom ha u; naba la wan ka por ka jingbishar jong u: bad to phin ïamane dem ïa uta uba la thaw ïa ka bneng bad ïa ka khyndew, bad ïa ka duriaw bad ïa ki pukri um.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad uwei pat u angel, u ba-ar, u la bud, u da ong, “La kyllon, la kyllon ka Babilon, kata ka nongbah ka bakhraw, kaba la pyndih ïa ki kynja bynriew baroh na ka Waiñ ka jingkhih bitar ka jingklim sih jong ka!”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u angel u balai u la bud ïa ki, u da ong da ka ktien bajam, “Lada uno uno ruh u mane dem ïa uta u mrad khlaw bad ïa ka dur jong u, bad u pdiang ïa kata ka dak halor ka shyllangmat jong u, lane halor ka kti jong u,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> uta ruh un dih na ka Waiñ ka jingbitar lep U Blei, ïa kaba la khreh khlem da pynkhleh ha kata ka khuri ka jingotshla jong u; bad yn pynkordit ïa u da ka ding bad da u kyndok ha khmat kita ki angel bakhuid, bad ha khmat uta U Khun langbrot:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> te ka tdem kata ka jingpynkordit ïa ki ka kiew noh sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut; bad kim ïoh ïa kaba shongthait mynsngi bad mynmiet, kiba ïamane dem ïa uta u mrad khlaw bad ïa ka dur jong u, bad jar uba pdiang ïa kata ka dak ka kyrteng jong u.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hangne ka don ka jingïaishah jong kita ki riewkhuid, kita kiba sumar ïa ki hukum U Blei, bad ïa ka jingngeit U Jisu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien na bneng kaba ong, “To thoh: Suk kita ki nongïap kiba ïap ha U Trai naduh mynta”: “Shisha,” ong U Mynsiem, “ba kin ïoh shongthait noh na ki jingtrei minot jong ki; naba kita ki jingleh jong ki, ki ïabud ryngkat bad ki.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad nga la ïohi, te ha khmih, u lyoh balieh; bad halor uta u lyoh u da shong uba kum U Khun u briew, uba don halor ka khlieh jong u ka pansngiat ksiar, bad ha ka kti jong u ka rashi banep.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad uwei pat u angel u la wan mih noh na ka ïing Blei, u da pyrta da ka ktien bajam ha uta uba shong halor uta u lyoh, “To phah noh ïa kata ka rashi jong me, bad to ot; naba kata ka aïom ban ot ka la wan, naba kata ka jingot ka khyndew ka la ih rkhiang.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te uta uba shong halor uta u lyoh u la buh ïa kata ka rashi jong u halor kata ka khyndew; kumta, la ot ïa kata ka khyndew.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad uwei pat u angel u la wan mih noh na kata ka templ kaba ha bneng, uba don ma u ruh ka rashi banep.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad uwei pat u angel u la wan mih noh na ka duwan, uba don ka bor halor ka ding; bad u la pyrta da ka jingpyrta bajam ha uta uba don kata ka rashi ka banep, u da ong, “To phah noh ïa kata ka rashi ka banep jong me, bad to lum ïa ki rynjup na u dieng soh Waiñ kata ka khyndew; naba ki soh Waiñ jong ka ki la ih bha.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te uta u angel u la buh ïa ka rashi jong u ha kata ka khyndew bad u la kheit ïa uta u dieng soh Waiñ jong kata ka khyndew, bad u la bred ïa ki sha ka jingtylliat umsoh kaba khraw jong ka jingbitar U Blei.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ïa kata ka jingtylliat umsoh la ïuh roit shabar kata ka nongbah, bad ka snam ka la mih noh na kata ka jingtylliat umsoh haduh ki lakam ki kulai, jin haduh arspah mail."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa kawei pat ka dak khyllah ha bneng, kaba khraw bad ba-iphylla, hynñiew angel kiba don hynñiew ki jingïapthem, kiba long ki bakhatduh; naba ha ki la pyndep noh ïa kata ka jingbitar U Blei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad nga la ïohi kum ïa ka duriaw ïit ïa kaba la khleh da ka ding; bad ïa kita kiba la ïoh ïa ka jingjopthiaw halor uta u mrad khlaw, bad halor kata ka dur jong u, bad halor kata ka dak jong u, bad halor kata ka jingkheiñ ka kyrteng jong u, ba ki da ïeng keiñ halor kata ka duriaw ïit, ki da don ruh ki duitara jong U Blei.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki ïarwai ïa ka jingrwai u Moses u shakri jong U Blei, bad ïa ka jingrwai jong uta U Khun langbrot, ki da ong, “Kiba khraw bad ba-iphylla long kita ki jingleh jong me, A U Trai uba U Blei Badonbor Baroh! ki bahok bad bashisha kita ki lynti jong me, U Syiem jong kita ki rta!",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Uei u ban ym tieng burom ïa me, A Trai, bad pyndonburom ïa ka kyrteng jong me? naba tang ma me hi u bakhuid. Naba ki kynja bynriew baroh kin ïawan bad kin ïamane dem ha khmat jong me, naba la pynpaw shynna ïa ki jingleh bahok jong me.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, nga la ïohi, bad ha khmih, la plie wang ïa ka templ jong Ka Tabernakl jong ka jingphla ha bneng;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad kita ki hynñiew angel kiba don kita ki hynñiew ki jingïapthem, ki la ïawan mih noh na kata ka templ, kiba la kup ïa ka jaiñ linen ka bakhuid bad ka batyngshaiñ, bad kiba la panpoh ha la ki shadem da ki jingpanpoh ksiar.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad uwei na kita ki jingthaw ba-im u la ai ha kita ki hynñiew angel, hynñiew ki pliang ksiar ba-dap da ka jingbitar U Blei u ba-im sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te la pyndap ïa kata ka templ da ka tdem na ka burom U Blei, bad na ka borbah jong u; te uno uno ruh um lah ban leit bsut sha kata ka templ, tad ynda la pyndep ïa kita ki hynñiew ki jingïapthem jong kita ki hynñiew angel."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien bajam na kata ka templ, kaba ong ha kita ki hynñiew angel, “To khie leit noh phi, bad to theh noh ïa kita ki pliang ka jingbitar U Blei ha kata ka khyndew.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u banyngkong u la leit noh, bad u la theh noh ïa ka pliang jong u halor kata ka khyndew; bad la long ka tohjaw basniew bad bashitom eh halor kita ki briew kiba don ka dak uta u mrad khlaw, bad kiba ïamane dem ïa ka dur jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad uta u ba-ar u la theh noh ïa ka pliang jong u sha kata ka duriaw; te ka la kylla long kum ka snam jong u baïap; bad ka mynsiem ba-im baroh ha kata ka duriaw ka la ïap noh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad uta u balai u la theh noh ïa ka pliang jong u sha kita ki wah bad sha kita ki pukri um; te ki la kylla long ka snam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew ïa uta u angel kita ki um ba u ong, “Me long u bahok, uba long bad uba la long, me U Bakhuid, naba me la kut bishar kumne:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> naba ki la ïa-pynmih noh ïa ka snam ki riewkhuid bad ki nongïathuhlypa, te me la ai ha ki ka snam ban dih: namar ki la kop hi kumta.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew na kata ka duwan kaba ong, “Shisha, ko Trai uba U Blei Badonbor Baroh, kiba shisha bad ki bahok long kita ki jingkut bishar jong me.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad uta u basaw u la theh noh ïa ka pliang jong u halor ka sngi; te la ai bor ha ka ban pynshit tyrha ïa ki briew da ka ding.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta keiñ, la pynshit tyrha ïa ki briew da ka jingshit ka bakhraw: te ki la ïakrenbeiñ ïa ka kyrteng jong uta U Blei uba don ka bor halor kine ki jingïapthem; te kim shym la kylla-ka-bamut ban ai burom ha u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad uta u basan u la theh noh ïa ka pliang jong u halor ka khet jong uta u mrad khlaw; te la pyndum noh ïa ka hima jong u; te ki la dait ïa la ki thylliej namar kata ka jingkordit,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad ki la ïakrenbeiñ ïa U Blei ka bneng namar kita ki jingkordit jong ki bad kita ki tohjaw jong ki; te kim shym la kylla-ka-bamut na ki jingleh jong ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad uta u bahynriew u la theh noh ïa ka pliang jong u halor kata ka wah bakhraw, ka Ïuphratis; te ka um jong ka, ka la rngad noh, ba yn ïoh khreh ïa ka lynti bah ïa ki syiem kiba na mihngi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad nga la ïohi lai tylli ki mynsiem bymkhuid kum ki jakoid kiba mih na ka shyntur uta u ïakjakor, bad na ka shyntur uta u mrad khlaw, bad na ka shyntur uta u nongïathuhlypa balamler;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> namar ki long ki mynsiem ki ksuid kiba leh ïa ki dak khyllah; kiba leit mih noh sha kita ki syiem jong kata ka pyrthei baroh kawei, ban ïalum lang ïa ki sha kata ka thma jong kata ka sngi ka bakhraw U Blei U Badonbor Baroh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> (“Ha khmih, nga wan kum u nongtuh. Suk uta uba sharai, bad uba ri noh ïa la ki jaiñkup, ïoh ba un ïaid lyngkhuit, bad ba kin ïohi ïa ka jinglehrain jong u.”)",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te ki ïalum lang ïa ki sha kata ka jaka ïa kaba la khot ha ka Hebru, “ka Armagedon”.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad uta u bahynñiew u la theh noh ïa ka pliang jong u sha ka suiñbneng; te ka la wan mih noh ka ktien bajam na kata ka templ, na kata ka khet, ka da ong, “La pyndep!”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te la don ki leilieh, bad ki jingsawa, bad ki pyrthat; bad la don ka jingkhynñiuh jumai bakhraw, kat kata kam ju la long naduh ba la long ki briew ha ka khyndew, ka jingkhynñiuh jumai bajur eh katta katta, bad kaba khraw katta katta.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te la pynbynta lai bynta ïa kata ka nongbah ka bakhraw, bad kita ki nongbah jong ki kynja bynriew ki la kyllon: bad la kynmaw ïa ka Babilon kaba khraw ha khmat U Blei, ban ai dih ha ka ïa kata ka khuri ka Waiñ ka jingshla ka jingbitar jong u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad kawei pa kawei ka 'dewlynnong ka la phet ïap noh, bad ïa ki lum ym shym la shem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u phria bakhraw, kat ka jingthew shi talent, u la hap na bneng halor ki briew: te ki briew ki la ïakrenbeiñ ïa U Blei namar kata ka jingïapthem jong u phria; naba kata ka jingïapthem jong u ka la long kaba khraw eh."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la wan uwei na kita ki hynñiew angel kiba la don kita ki hynñiew pliang, bad u la kren bad nga, u da ong, “To ale shane, ngan pyni ha me ïa ka jingpynrem ïa kata ka nuti kaba khraw kaba shong halor shibun ki um;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ka kita ki syiem jong ka khyndew ki la ïaklim sih, bad la pynbuaid ïa kita kiba shong ha ka khyndew da ka Waiñ kata ka jingklim sih jong ka.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u la rah noh ïa nga ha U Mynsiem sha ka ri khlaw: bad nga la ïohi ïa ka briew kaba shong halor u mrad khlaw basaw hain, ba dap da ki kyrteng ka jingkrenbeiñ Blei, uba don hynñiew ki khlieh bad shiphew ki reng.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ïa kata ka briew la pynkup jaiñ basaw bthuh bad basaw hain, bad la pyndeng ïa ka da ka ksiar, bad da u maw bakordor, bad da ki paila, ka da bat ïa ka khuri ksiar ha ka kti jong ka, kaba dap da ki jingijli bad ka jingbymkhuid kata ka jingklim sih jong ka;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad halor ka shyllangmat jong ka, la don ka kyrteng ïa kaba la thoh, “Ka Jingmaïan, ka Babilon ka bakhraw, ka kmie kita ki nuti bad kita ki jingijli jong kata ka khyndew.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa kata ka briew ba ka buaid da ka snam jong kita ki riewkhuid, bad da ka snam kita ki nongphla ba shahïap jong U Jisu: Te haba nga la ïohi ïa ka, nga la sngewphylla da ka jingsngewphylla bakhraw.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te uta u angel u la ong ha nga, “Hato balei me la sngewphylla? ngan ïathuh ha me ïa kata ka jingmaïan jong kata ka briew, bad ka jong uta u mrad khlaw uba kit ïa ka, uba don kita ki hynñiew ki khlieh bad kita ki shiphew ki reng.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Uta u mrad khlaw ïa uba me la ïohi u la long, bad um long shuh; te u ban sa kiew noh na kata ka 'liewlong bakhlem trai, bad u ban leit noh sha ka jingpynjot. Te kita kiba shong halor kata ka khyndew kin ïasngewkyndit (ïa kiba ki kyrteng jong ki ym shym la thoh ha kata ka kitab jong ka jingim na myndanglong ka pyrthei), haba ki ïakhmih ïa uta u mrad khlaw kumno ba u la ju long, bad ba um long shuh, bad ba un sa long.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hangne don ka jingmut kaba don ka jingstad. Kita ki hynñiew ki khlieh ki long hynñiew ki lum, ha kiba kata ka briew ka shong.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki long hynñiew ki syiem; ki san ngut ki la hap, bad uta uwei u long, te uta uwei pat um pat la wan; bad ynda u wan, ka dei ïa u ban sah katto katne.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te uta u mrad khlaw uba la ju long, bad um long shuh, uta hi u long u baphra ruh, bad u long na kita ki hynñiew; bad u leit noh sha ka jingpynjot.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad kita ki shiphew reng ïa kiba me la ïohi, ki long shiphew ki syiem ki bym pat shym la pdiang ïa ka hima; hynrei, ki ïa-pdiang ïa ka bor kum ki syiem, ïa tang shi por, lem bad uta u mrad khlaw.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kine ki ïadon kawei ka jingmut, te ki ïa-aiti ïa ka bor bad ïa ka bor synshar jong ki ha uta u mrad khlaw.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kine kin ïaleh thma bad uta U Khun langbrot, bad uta U Khun langbrot un jop noh ïa ki, naba u long U Trai ki trai, bad U Syiem ki syiem; kumjuh ruh kita kiba don lem bad u, ïa kiba la khot, bad ïa kiba la jied bad kiba ïaineh.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u la ong ha nga, “Kita ki um ïa kiba me la ïohi, ha kaba kata ka nuti ka shong, ki long ki paidlang, bad ki paidbah, bad ki kynja bynriew, bad ki thylliej.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad kita ki shiphew ki reng ïa kiba me la ïohi, bad uta u mrad khlaw, kine kin ïashun ïa kata ka nuti, bad kin ïa-pynlong kaba marwei bad ka balyngkhuit ïa ka, bad kin ïabam duh ïa ka doh jong ka, bad kin ïathang duh ïa ka da ka ding.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Namar U Blei u la buh ha ki dohnud jong ki ban leh ïa ka mon jong u, bad ban ïakut da kawei ka jingmut, bad ban ïa-aiti ïa ka hima jong ki ha uta u mrad khlaw, tad ynda yn pyndep noh ïa kita ki ktien U Blei.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te kata ka briew ïa kaba me la ïohi, ka long kata ka nongbah kaba khraw kaba synshar halor kita ki syiem kata ka khyndew.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, nga la ïohi ïa uwei pat u angel uba wan hiar na bneng, uba don ka bor bakhraw; ba la pynshai ïa ka khyndew da ka burom jong u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la pyrta da ka ktien bajam, u da ong, “La kyllon, la kyllon ka Babilon kaba khraw, te ka la jia long ka jaka shong ki ksuid bad ka jaka ri ka mynsiem bymkhuid baroh, bad ka jaka ri ka sim bymkhuid bad ba-isaitmet baroh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Naba da ka Waiñ ka jingkhih bitar ka jingklim sih jong ka, la pynkyllon ïa ki kynja bynriew baroh; bad kita ki syiem jong kata ka khyndew ki la ïaklim sih bad ka, bad ki nongkhaïi jong kata ka khyndew ki la ïaman riewbha da ka bor ka jingleh pahuh jong ka.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te nga la ïohsngew ïa kawei pat ka ktien na bneng, ka da ong, “To ïamih noh na ka, u paidlang jong nga, ba phin ym ïashang lem bad kita ki pop jong ka, bad ba phin ym ïa-pdiang na kita ki jingïapthem jong ka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Naba kita ki pop jong ka ki la ïakot haduh ka bneng, bad U Blei u la kynmaw ïa kita ki jingleh bymman jong ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> To phin leh keiñ ha ka kumba ma ka ruh ka la leh, bad to phin leh ar shah ha ka, ïa kaba ar shah keiñ, katba kum kita ki jingleh jong ka; ha kata ka khuri ïa kaba ka la khleh, to phin khleh ha ka ïa kaba ar shah keiñ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Katno katno ba ka la pyndonburom ïa lade, bad ka la im pahuh hai, katta keiñ ka jingkordit bad ka jingsngewsih to phin ai ha ka: naba ka ong ha la ka dohnud, ‘Nga shong ka syiem, bad ngam long ka riewkynthei, bad ngan ym da ïohi ïa ka jingsngewsih satia.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Namar kane, kita ki jingïapthem jong ka kin ïawan ha kawei ka sngi, ka jingïap, bad ka jingsngewsih, bad ka 'nemsniew: bad yn thang duh ïa ka da ka ding; naba u bakhrawbor long U Trai uba U Blei uba bishar ïa ka.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te kita ki syiem jong kata ka khyndew, kiba la ïaklim sih bad kiba la ïa-im pahuh hai bad ka, kin ïaïam, bad kin ïalynñiar lympat na ka bynta jong ka, ynda kin ïakhmih ïa ka tdem ka jingpluh jong ka,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> haba ki ïeng na sha jngai namar kata ka jingsheptieng ïa ka jingkordit jong ka, ki da ïa-ong, “Kordit, kordit, kata ka nongbah ka bakhraw, ka Babilon, kata ka nongbah kaba don bor! naba ha kaba shi por ka la poi kata ka jingshitom jong pha.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki nongkhaïi jong kata ka khyndew ki ïaïam bad ki ïasngewsih namar jong ka, naba ym don ba thied shuh ïa ka jingkhaïi jong ki;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ïa ka jingkhaïi ka ksiar, bad ka rupa, bad u maw bakordor, bad ki paila, bad ka jaiñ linen bani, bad ka jaiñ basaw bthuh, bad ka jaiñ muka, bad ka jaiñ basaw hain, bad ka dieng baroh baiwbih, bad ka kynja pliang bniat hati baroh, bad ka pliang baroh ba thaw na ka dieng bakordor tam, bad ka rnong, bad u nar, bad u mawleiñ,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> bad ka sisia, bad ki musla, bad kiba thang iwbih, bad ka jingsleh, bad ka jingiwbih, bad ka Waiñ, bad ka umphniang Olib, bad u 'purew bani, bad u Kew, bad ki masi, bad ki langbrot, bad ki kulai, bad ki kali, bad ki mraw, bad ki mynsiem ki briew.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> “Te kita ki soh ba ka mynsiem jong pha ka la thrang ki la leit noh na pha, bad kita kiei kiei baroh kiba shngiam bad kiba pahuh hai, ki la ïajah noh na pha; bad da lei lei phan ym shem shuh ïa ki.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kita ki nongkhaïi ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, ïa kiba la pynriewspah na ka, kin ïaïeng na sha jngai, namar kaba sheptieng ïa ka jingkordit jong ka, ki da ïaïam bad ki da ïasngewsih;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ki da ïa-ong, “Kordit, kordit, kata ka nongbah ka bakhraw, ïa kaba la pynkup ha ka jaiñ linen bani bad jaiñ basaw bthuh bad jaiñ basaw hain, bad ïa kaba la pyndeng da ka ksiar bad da u maw bakordor bad da ki paila! naba ha kaba shi por la pynduh noh khoit ïa kata ka spah kaba khraw eh katta katta.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u maji baroh, bad u paidlang baroh halor kita ki lieng, bad ki riewlieng, bad kat kiba ïoh la ka bam na ka duriaw, ki la ïaïeng na sha jngai,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ki la ïalynñiar haba ki la ïakhmih ïa ka tdem ka jingpluh jong ka, ki da ïa-ong, “Kano ka nongbah kaba kum katai ka nongbah kaba khraw?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki la ïakynting ïa ka 'dewmet halor ki khlieh jong ki, bad ki la ïakyang da kaba ïam bad basngewsih, ki da ïa-ong, “Kordit, kordit, kata ka nongbah kaba khraw, ha kaba la pynriewspah ïa kita baroh kiba don ki lieng ha kata ka duriaw, na jong kata ka jingkordor jong ka! naba ha kaba shi por la pynduh noh khoit ïa ka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> To phan leh kmen halor jong ka, ko ka bneng, bad phi ki riewkhuid, bad phi ki apostol, bad ki nongïathuhlypa; naba U Blei u la bishar ïa ka jingtian bishar jong phi halor jong ka.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te uwei u angel uba don bor u la rah ïa u maw kum u mawtylliat bakhraw, bad u la pynnoh ïa u sha ka duriaw, u da ong, “Kumne da ka bor kyrthep yn pynnoh ïa ka Babilon, kata ka nongbah kaba khraw, bad da lei lei yn ym shem shuh ïa ka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ïa ka jingsawa jong ki nongtem duitara, bad jong ki nongrwai, bad jong ki duhalia, bad jong ki nongput turoi, da lei lei yn ym ïohsngew shuh ha pha; bad ïa u nongkam stad baroh, la kano kano ka jingkam stad, da lei lei yn ym shem shuh ha pha; bad ïa ka jingsawa u mawtylliat, da lei lei yn ym ïohsngew shuh ha pha;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> bad ïa ka jingshai ka sharak da lei lei yn ym pynshai shuh ha pha; bad ïa ka jingsawa u nongleit-kurim bad ka nongleit-kurim da lei lei yn ym ïohsngew shuh ha pha; naba kita ki nongkhaïi jong pha ki la ju ïalong ki bakhraw batri jong ka khyndew; naba da kata kaba ai ksuid jong pha la shukor noh ïa ki kynja bynriew baroh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ha ka la shem ïa ka snam jong ki nongïathuhlypa bad jong ki riewkhuid, bad ka jong kita baroh ïa kiba la pynïap noh ha ka khyndew.”"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, nga la ïohsngew kum ka ktien bajam u paidbah byllien ha bneng, ka da ong, “Halleluïa! Ka Jingpynim, bad ka burom, bad ka bor, ki long ki jong U Blei jong ngi!",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Naba kiba shisha bad ki bahok long kita ki jingbishar jong u; naba u la bishar ïa kata ka nuti ka bakhraw, kaba la ju pynpyut ïa kata ka khyndew da ka jingleh nuti jong ka, bad u pynhiar kput ïa ka na ka bynta ka snam kita ki shakri jong u.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki la ïa-ong pat, “Halleluïa! Bad ka tdem jong ka te ka kiew noh sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad kita ki arphew saw ngut ki tymmen basan bad kita ki saw ki jingthaw ba-im ki la ïahap dem bad ki la ïamane ïa U Blei u bashong halor kata ka khet, ki da ïa-ong, “Amen; Halleluïa!”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ka ktien sawa ka la wan mih noh na kata ka khet, ka da ong, “To ïaroh ïa U Blei jong ngi, phi baroh ki shakri jong u, bad phi kiba sheptieng ïa u, ki barit baraiñ ruh bad ki bakhraw batri.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew kum ka jingsawa u paidbah byllien, bad kum ka jingsawa shibun ki um, bad kum ka jingsawa ki pyrthat bajam, ki da ong, “Halleluïa! naba U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi, U Badonbor Baroh, u la synshar.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> To ngin ïakmen bad ngin ïashadkmen, bad to ngin ïa-ai ka burom ha u: naba ka jingshongkurim U Khun langbrot ka la jia, bad ka tnga jong u ka la pynkhreh ïa lade.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te la ai ha ka ba kan da ïoh kup ïa ka jaiñ linen bani, bakhuid bad batyngshain:” Namar kata ka jaiñ linen bani ka long keiñ ki jinglehhok jong ki riewkhuid.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u ong ha nga, “To thoh: Suk kita ïa kiba la khot sha kata ka jingïakhawai miet ka jingshongkurim uta U Khun langbrot.” U ong ruh ha nga, “Kine ki long ki ktien bashisha ki jong U Blei.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te nga la hap dem ha khmat ki kjat jong u ban mane dem ha u. Te u ong ha nga, “To sumar me, wat leh ïa kata! nga long u para shakri jong me bad jong kita ki parabangeit jong me kiba bat ïa ka jingphla U Jisu. To mane dem ïa U Blei” (namar kata ka jingphla U Jisu ka long ka mynsiem ka jingïathuhlypa).",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa ka bneng ba la plie, bad ha khmih ka kulai balieh; bad ïa uta uba shong halor jong ka la khot U Baïaineh bad U Bashisha; bad ha ka hok, u bishar bad u ïaleh thma.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki khmat jong u ki kum ka thylliej ka ding, bad halor ka khlieh jong u don ki pansngiat shibun: u don ruh ka kyrteng ba la thoh, ïa kaba uno uno ruh um ithuh, hynrei, tang ma u hi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad la pynkup ïa u da ka jaiñkup ïa kaba la wieh ha ka snam: bad la khot ïa ka kyrteng jong u, “U Ktien jong U Blei”.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad kita ki paidïapom kiba ha bneng ki la ïabud ïa u halor ki kulai balieh, kiba la kup da ka jaiñ linen bani, ka balieh bad bakhuid.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad na ka shyntur jong u ka mih noh ka waitlam banep, bad da kata un da shoh ïa ki kynja bynriew: te un synshar ïa ki da u dieng synshar nar: bad u ïuh roit ïa ka jingtylliat umsoh ka jingshla ka jong ka jingbitar U Blei U Badonbor Baroh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u don halor ka jaiñkup, bad halor ka lbong jong u, ka kyrteng ba la thoh, “U Syiem Ki Syiem bad U Trai Ki Trai”.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa uwei u angel uba ïeng ha ka sngi; bad u la pyrta da ka ktien bajam, u da ong ha kita ki sim baroh ki baher hapdeng ka suiñ, “To ale, bad to phin ïalang sha ka jingïakhawai miet kaba khraw jong U Blei;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> khnang ba phin ïoh bam ïa ka doh ki syiem, bad ïa ka doh ki rangbah shihajar, bad ïa ka doh ki bakhlaiñ, bad ïa ka doh ki kulai bad ïa ka jong kita kiba shong halor jong ki, bad ïa ka doh ki bynriew baroh, kiba laitluid ruh bad ki mraw, ki barit ruh bad ki bakhraw.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa uta u mrad khlaw, bad ïa kita ki syiem jong ka khyndew, bad ïa kita ki paidïapom jong ki, kiba la ïaseng lang ban ïaleh thma ïa uta uba shong halor kata ka kulai, bad ïa uta u paidïapom jong u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te la kem ïa uta u mrad khlaw, bad lem bad u ruh ïa uta u nongïathuhlypa balamler uba la leh ïa kita ki dak khyllah ha khmat jong u, da kiba u la shukor ïa kita kiba la pdiang ïa kata ka dak uta u mrad khlaw, bad ïa kita kiba la ïamane dem ïa kata ka dur jong u. Ïa kine baroh ar, la bred im keiñ sha kata ka pung ka ding ïa kaba la thang da u kyndok.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ïa kita kiba sah la pynïap noh da kata ka waitlam jong uta uba shong halor kata ka kulai, kata ka waitlam keiñ kaba mih noh na ka shyntur jong u: te ïa kita ki sim baroh la pynkdang da ka doh jong ki."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa u angel ba u wan hiar na bneng, uba don uta u shabi kata ka 'liewlong bakhlem trai bad u kynjri bakhraw ha ka kti jong u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la kem ïa uta u ïakjakor, ïa uta u bseiñ batymmen, uba long u Ksuid bad u Soitan, bad u la khum ïa u, shi hajar snem;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad u la bred ïa u sha kata ka 'liewlong bakhlem trai, bad u la set ïa ka, bad u la shon shab ïa ka halor jong u, khnang ba un ym ïoh shukor shuh ïa ki kynja bynriew tad ynda la pyndep ïa kata ka shi hajar snem; te hadien kata keiñ ka dei ban pyllait noh ïa u shi por.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa ki khet, bad don kiba la shong halor jong ki, bad la ai ka jingbishar ha ki; bad nga la ïohi ïa ki mynsiem jong kita ïa kiba la khrai khlieh na ka bynta kata ka jingphla ïa U Jisu, bad na ka bynta ka ktien U Blei, bad jar ki bym shym la ïamane dem ïa uta u mrad khlaw, lymne ïa ka dur jong u, bad kim shym la pdiang ïa kata ka dak halor ka shyllangmat jong ki bad halor ka kti jong ki; te ki la im, bad ki la synshar lem bad U Khrist, shi hajar snem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, kita kiba sah na kita ki baïap kim shym la im pat tad ynda la pyndep ïa kata ka shi hajar snem. Kane ka long ka jingmihpat ka banyngkong.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Uba suk bad u bakhuid long uta uba don ka bynta ha kata ka jingmihpat ka banyngkong: halor kine, kata ka jingïap ka ba-ar kam don bor shuh; hynrei, kin long ki lyngdoh jong U Blei bad jong U Khrist, bad kin ïasynshar lem bad u, shi hajar snem.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ynda la pyndep ïa kata ka shi hajar snem, yn pyllait noh ïa uta u Soitan na ka byndi jong u,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad un leit mih noh ban shukor ïa kita ki kynja bynriew kiba ha kita ki sawdong ka pyrthei, ïa u Gog bad ïa u Magog, ban pynïaseng lang ïa ki sha kata ka thma; ka jingkheiñ jong kita ka long kum u shyiap ka duriaw.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki la ïaleit kiew halor ka pyngkiang ka khyndew, bad ki la ïaker tawiar ïa ka jaka shong dara kita ki riewkhuid, bad ïa kata ka nongbah ïa kaba la ieit: te ka ding ka la wan hiar na U Blei na bneng, bad ka la bam duh ïa ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ïa uta u Soitan uba shukor ïa ki la bred keiñ sha kata ka pung ka ding bad u kyndok, ha kaba ki don ruh uta u mrad khlaw bad uta u nongïathuhlypa balamler; bad yn pynkordit ïa ki, mynsngi bad mynmiet, sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa ka khet balieh bakhraw, bad ïa uta uba shong halor jong ka, na khmat jong u, ba ka khyndew bad ka bneng ki la ïaphet noh; te ïa ka jaka ym shym la shem shuh ïa ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa ki baïap, ki barit bad ki bakhraw, ba ki da ïeng ha khmat kata ka khet; bad la plied ïa ki kitab: bad la plied ïa kawei pat ka kitab, kaba long ka kitab ka jingim: te la bishar ïa kita ki baïap na kita kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba la thoh ha kita ki kitab, katba kum ki jingleh jong ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ka duriaw ka la aiti noh ïa ki baïap kiba la don ha ka; bad ka Jingïap bad ka Hades ki la aiti noh ïa kita ki baïap kiba la don ha ki; te la bishar ïa uwei pa uwei baroh katba kum ki jingleh jong ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ïa ka Jingïap bad ka Hades la bred sha kata ka pung ka ding. Kane ka long kata ka jingïap ka ba-ar, kata ka pung ka ding keiñ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te jar ïa uba ym shym la shem ba la thoh ha kata ka kitab ka jingim, la bred ïa u sha kata ka pung ka ding."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa ka bneng bathymmai bad ïa ka khyndew bathymmai; namar kata ka bneng banyngkong bad kata ka khyndew banyngkong ki la leit noh; bad ka duriaw kam don shuh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad nga la ïohi ïa ka nongbah ka bakhuid, ka Jerusalem bathymmai, ba ka da wan hiar na U Blei na bneng, ïa kaba la khreh kum ka nongleit-kurim ïa kaba la pynibha khnang ïa u tnga jong ka.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew ka ktien bajam na kata ka khet, ka da ong, “Ha khmih, Ka Tabernakl U Blei ryngkat bad ki briew, bad un shong lem bad ki, te ma ki kin ïalong ki paidlang jong u, bad U Blei hi un long lem bad ki, bad un long U Blei jong ki:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> te U Blei un ñiad noh ïa ka jingjaw ummat baroh na ki khmat jong ki; bad ka jingïap kan ym long shuh, lymne ka jingsngewsih, lymne ka jingïam, lymne ka jingpang, kan ym long shuh: kita kiei kiei kiba mynshuwa ki la leit noh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te uta u bashong halor kata ka khet u la ong, “Ha khmih, nga thaw thymmai ïa kiei kiei baroh.” Bad u ong, “To thoh: naba kine ki ktien ki long kiba ïaineh bad bashisha.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la ong ha nga, “La pyndep. Nga long ma nga U Alpha bad U Omega, u basdang bad u bakut. Ha uta u basliang ngan ai ei na ka jong kata ka pukri ka um ka jingim.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Uta uba jop un ïoh ïa kiei kiei baroh; bad ngan long U Blei jong u, bad ma u de un long u khun jong nga.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, ïa kita kiba sheptieng, bad ïa ki bymngeit, bad ïa kiba ijli, bad ïa kiba pynïap bad ïa kiba kyr-eit, bad ïa kiba ai ksuid, bad ïa kiba mane bleithaw, bad ïa kita baroh kiba lamler, ka bynta jong ki kan long ha kata ka pung ïa kaba thang da ka ding bad da u kyndok; kaba long kata ka jingïap ka ba-ar.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te la wan ha nga uwei na kita ki hynñiew angel kiba don kita ki hynñiew pliang, kiba dap da kita ki hynñiew ki jingïapthem ki bakhatduh; bad u la kren bad nga, u da ong, “To ale shane, ngan pyni ha me ïa kata ka nongleit-kurim, kaba ka tnga uta U Khun langbrot.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u la rah noh ïa nga ha U Mynsiem shalor u lum bakhraw bad bajrong, bad u la kdew ha nga ïa kata ka nongbah ka bakhuid, ka Jerusalem keiñ, ba ka wan hiar na bneng na U Blei,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ka da don ka burom U Blei: ka jingshai jong ka, kaba kum u maw bakordor tam, kum u maw Jasper basngur eh, kum u Mawleiñ:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ka da don ruh ka kynroh bakhraw bad bajrong; ka da don khat-ar ki khyrdop, bad ha kita ki khyrdop, khat-ar ki angel; bad ki kyrteng ïa kiba la thoh halor jong ki, kiba long ki kyrteng jong kita ki khat-ar jaid ki khun Israel:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na phang mihngi, lai ki khyrdop; na phang shatei, lai ki khyrdop; na phang shathie, lai ki khyrdop; bad na phang sepngi, lai ki khyrdop.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad kata ka kynroh jong kata ka nongbah ka la don khat-ar ki nongrim, bad halor jong ki, ki kyrteng kita ki khat-ar ngut ki apostol jong uta U Khun langbrot.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te uta uba kren bad nga u la don u dieng thew da u stew ksiar ba un thew ïa kata ka nongbah, bad ïa kita ki khyrdop jong ka, bad ïa kata ka kynroh jong ka.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ïa kata ka nongbah la pynlong kaba sawdong, te ka lynter jong ka, ka long kat ka pyngkiang: bad u la thew ïa kata ka nongbah da uta u stew, jin khatsan spah mail: ka lynter bad ka pyngkiang bad ka jingjrong jong ka, ki ïalong marryngkat.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la thew ïa kata ka kynroh jong ka, shispah sawphew saw pruh, katba kum ka jingthew u briew, kaba long ka jong u angel.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ka jingtei ïa kata ka kynroh jong ka, ka long da u maw Jasper; bad kata ka nongbah ka la long ka ksiar banylla, kaba kum ka ïit basngur.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ïa kita ki nongrim kata ka kynroh jong kata ka nongbah la pynibha da ki har rukom ki mawkordor. Kata ka nongrim ka banyngkong ka la long da u maw Jasper; kata ka ba-ar, da u Sapheiros; kata ka balai, da u Kalkedon; kata ka basaw, da u Emerald;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> kata ka basan, da u Sardonyks; kata ka bahynriew, da u Sardios; kata ka bahynñiew, da u Khyrsoleit; kata ka baphra, da u Beryl; kata ka bakhyndai, da u Topas; kata ka bashiphew, da u Khrusoprasos; kata ka bakhatwei, da u Hyakinthos; kata ka bakhat-ar, da u Amethyst.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad kita ki khat-ar ki khyrdop ki la long khat-ar ki paila; kawei kawei keiñ na kita ki khyrdop ka la long na u paila tylli: bad ka lynti bah jong kata ka nongbah ka la long ka ksiar banylla, kum ka ïit bashai lyngba.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ïa ka templ ngam shym la ïohi ha ka: namar U Trai uba U Blei U Badonbor Baroh, bad uta U Khun langbrot, ki long ka templ jong ka.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad kata ka nongbah kam donkam ïa ka sngi, lymne ïa u bnai ban pynshai ha ka: namar ka burom U Blei ka la pynshai ïa ka, bad ka jingshai jong ka long uta U Khun langbrot.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad kita ki kynja bynriew kin ïa-ïaid ha kata ka jingshai jong ka: bad ki syiem ka khyndew ki wallam ïa ka burom jong ki sha ka.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ïa kita ki khyrdop jong ka yn ym khang satia mynsngi (namar ka miet kan ym long hangta):",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> bad kin wallam ïa ka burom bad ïa ka jingpyndonburom jong kita ki kynja bynriew sha ka.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad da lei lei kan ym ïoh leit bsut sha ka kaei kaei ruh ka bymkhuid, lane uta uba leh ïa ka jingijli bad ka jinglamler: hynrei, tang kita keiñ ïa kiba la thoh ha kata ka kitab ka jingim jong uta U Khun langbrot."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u la pyni ha nga ïa ka wah basngur ka um ka jingim, kaba phyrnai kum u mawleiñ, kaba mih noh na ka khet U Blei bad ka jong uta U Khun langbrot, hapdeng kata ka lynti bah jong ka.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ha baroh ar liang jong kata ka wah la don u dieng ka jingim, uba sei noh ïa ki khat-ar ki jingsei soh, ha la u bnai u da sei noh ïa kata ka jingsei soh jong ka: bad ki sla jong uta u dieng ki long ïa ka ban pynkhiah ïa ki kynja bynriew.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ka jingtim baroh kan ym long shuh: bad kata ka khet jong U Blei bad jong uta U Khun langbrot kan long ha ka: bad ki shakri jong u kin ïashakri ïa u;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad kin ïohi ïa ka khmat jong u; bad ka kyrteng jong u kan long halor ki shyllangmat jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ka miet kan ym long shuh; te kim donkam ïa ka jingshai ka sharak, lymne ïa ka jingshai ka sngi; naba U Trai uba U Blei un pynshai ha ki, bad kin synshar sha ki bymjukut ki bymjukut.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u la ong ha nga, “Kine ki ktien ki long kiba ïaineh bad bashisha: bad uta U Trai uba U Blei jong kita ki mynsiem ki nongïathuhlypa, u la phah ïa u angel jong u ban pyni ha ki shakri jong u ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba dei ban jia long shen.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> “Ha khmih nga wan kloi: suk uta uba ïaisumar ïa ki ktien jong ka jingïathuhlypa kane ka kitab.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ma nga u Ïoannis nga long uta uba la ïohsngew bad uba la ïohi ïa kine kiei kiei ruh. Te mynba nga la ïohsngew bad nga la ïohi, nga la hap dem ban mane ha khmat ki kjat uta u angel uba la pyni ha nga ïa kine kiei kiei ruh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u ong ha nga, “To sumar me, wat leh ïa kata! namar nga long u para shakri jong me bad jong kita ki parabangeit jong me ki nongïathuhlypa, bad jong kita kiba ïasumar ïa ki ktien jong kane ka kitab: to mane dem ïa U Blei.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u ong ha nga, “To me wat pyndait laha ïa kita ki ktien jong ki jingïathuhlypa kane ka kitab; naba kata ka Ïa ka long hajan.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Uta u bymhok, to un nang leh bymhok: bad uta uba tngit, to un nang tngit: bad uta u bahok, to un nang leh hok: bad uta u bakhuid, to un nang khuid.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Ha khmih nga wan kloi; bad ka nong jong nga ka don lem bad nga, ban ai nong ha uwei pa uwei baroh kat kumba long ka jingleh jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nga long ma nga U Alpha bad U Omega, u banyngkong bad u bakhatduh, u basdang bad u bakut.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Suk kita kiba la sait ïa la ki jaiñkup, ba kin ïoh ka hok ban wan sha uta u dieng ka jingim, bad kin ïoh leit bsut da kita ki khyrdop sha kata ka nongbah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Shabar ki long kita ki ksew, bad kita kiba ai ksuid, bad kita kiba kyr-eit bad kita kiba pynïap, bad kita kiba mane bleithaw, bad baroh kat kiba ieit bad bathaw ïa ka lamler.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Ma nga, U Jisu, nga la phah ïa u angel jong nga ban phla ha phi ïa kine kiei kiei ruh na ka bynta kita ki balang: Nga long ma nga U Thied bad U Khun u ksiew u Dabid, bad uta U Khlur-step batyngshaiñ.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te U Mynsiem bad kata ka nongleit-kurim ki ïa-ong, “To wan.” Bad uta uba ïohsngew to un ong, “To wan.” Bad jar uba sliang, to ai un wan: bad jar uba mon, to un shim ei ïa ka um ka jingim.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nga phla ha uwei pa uwei baroh uba ïohsngew ïa ki ktien jong ka jingïathuhlypa kane ka kitab: Lada uei uei ruh un da pynlang ha kine, U Blei un pynlang ha uta ïa kita ki jingïapthem ïa kiba la thoh ha kane ka kitab:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> te lada uno uno ruh un shim noh na kita ki ktien ka kitab jong kane ka jingïathuhlypa, U Blei un shim noh ïa ka bynta jong u na u dieng ka jingim, bad na kata ka nongbah ka bakhuid, bad na kita kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba la thoh ha kane ka kitab.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Uta uba phla ïa kine kiei kiei ruh u ong, “Shisha: nga wan kloi.” Amen, to wan, Trai Jisu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ka jingaiei ka jong U Jisu Khrist uba U Trai jong ngi to kan long lem bad kita ki riewkhuid. Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;